<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Error Rates>
We are investigating increased error rates for Autoscaling API calls in the US-GOV-WEST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Error Rates>
Between 11:43 AM and 12:48 PM PDT we experienced increased error rates for Autoscaling API calls in the US-GOV-WEST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
